query.esql:
FROM logs-*
| WHERE data_stream.dataset == "mysqlreceiver.otel"
    AND event_name == "db.server.top_query"
    AND @timestamp >= ?_tstart 
    AND @timestamp < ?_tend
| STATS 
    unique_queries = COUNT_DISTINCT(mysql.events_statements_summary_by_digest.digest),
    total_calls = SUM(mysql.events_statements_summary_by_digest.count_star),
    total_time_sec = SUM(mysql.events_statements_summary_by_digest.sum_timer_wait)
| EVAL avg_time_ms = CASE(total_calls > 0, total_time_sec / total_calls * 1000, 0.0)
| KEEP unique_queries, total_calls, total_time_sec, avg_time_ms

query.esql:
FROM logs-*
| WHERE data_stream.dataset == "mysqlreceiver.otel"
    AND event_name == "db.server.query_sample"
    AND @timestamp >= NOW() - 1 minute
| EVAL is_lock_wait = CASE(mysql.wait_type LIKE "%lock%", 1, 0)
| STATS 
    active_queries = COUNT(*),
    max_wait_time = MAX(mysql.events_waits_current.timer_wait),
    waiting_on_lock = SUM(is_lock_wait)
| KEEP active_queries, max_wait_time, waiting_on_lock
